  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this research study is to evaluate an investigational system that may allow
      doctors to show images of the different parts inside the eye that show greater detail than
      current equipment can produce.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this research study is to evaluate an investigational system that may allow
      doctors to make images of the parts inside the eye that show greater detail than current
      equipment can produce.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
